author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
🎟️ To see Justin Hawkins Rides Again LIVE across the UK, visit:

I haven't been around much recently as I've been on tour in the USA and Europe with The Darkness. On my way home, I played piano at St Pancras Station and went to Salford for an interview with  BBC Breakfast about next year's Arena Tour. I nailed it!

To see more from JHRA,  join my Patreon here: http://www.patreon.com/jushawk
